19 * Scripts for spells with SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC spells used for quests.
20 * Ordered alphabetically using questId and scriptname.
21 * Scriptnames of files in this file should be prefixed with "spell_q#questID_".
22 */

35class spell_generic_quest_update_entry_SpellScript : public SpellScript
36{
37 PrepareSpellScript(spell_generic_quest_update_entry_SpellScript);
38 private:
39 uint16 _spellEffect;
40 uint8 _effIndex;
41 uint32 _originalEntry;
42 uint32 _newEntry;
43 bool _shouldAttack;
44 uint32 _despawnTime;
45
46 public:
47 spell_generic_quest_update_entry_SpellScript(uint16 spellEffect, uint8 effIndex, uint32 originalEntry, uint32 newEntry, bool shouldAttack, uint32 despawnTime = 0) :
48 SpellScript(), _spellEffect(spellEffect), _effIndex(effIndex), _originalEntry(originalEntry),
49 _newEntry(newEntry), _shouldAttack(shouldAttack), _despawnTime(despawnTime) { }
50
51 void HandleDummy(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
52 {
53 if (Creature* creatureTarget = GetHitCreature())
54 if (!creatureTarget->IsPet() && creatureTarget->GetEntry() == _originalEntry)
55 {
56 creatureTarget->UpdateEntry(_newEntry);
57 if (_shouldAttack && creatureTarget->IsAIEnabled)
58 creatureTarget->AI()->AttackStart(GetCaster());
59
60 if (_despawnTime)
61 creatureTarget->DespawnOrUnsummon(_despawnTime);
62 }
63 }
64
65 void Register() override
66 {
67 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_generic_quest_update_entry_SpellScript::HandleDummy, _effIndex, _spellEffect);
68 }
69};

179// http://www.wowhead.com/quest=6124 Curing the Sick (A)
180// http://www.wowhead.com/quest=6129 Curing the Sick (H)
181// 19512 Apply Salve
182enum Quests6124_6129Data
183{
184 NPC_SICKLY_GAZELLE = 12296,
185 NPC_CURED_GAZELLE = 12297,
186 NPC_SICKLY_DEER = 12298,
187 NPC_CURED_DEER = 12299,
188 DESPAWN_TIME = 30000
189};
190
191class spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve : public SpellScriptLoader
192{
193 public:
194 spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve") { }
195
196 class spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve_SpellScript : public SpellScript
197 {
198 PrepareSpellScript(spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve_SpellScript);
199
200 bool Load() override
201 {
202 return GetCaster()->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER;
203 }
204
205 void HandleDummy(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
206 {
207 Player* caster = GetCaster()->ToPlayer();
208 if (GetCastItem())
209 if (Creature* creatureTarget = GetHitCreature())
210 {
211 uint32 newEntry = 0;
212 switch (caster->GetTeam())
213 {
214 case HORDE:
215 if (creatureTarget->GetEntry() == NPC_SICKLY_GAZELLE)
216 newEntry = NPC_CURED_GAZELLE;
217 break;
218 case ALLIANCE:
219 if (creatureTarget->GetEntry() == NPC_SICKLY_DEER)
220 newEntry = NPC_CURED_DEER;
221 break;
222 }
223 if (newEntry)
224 {
225 creatureTarget->UpdateEntry(newEntry);
226 creatureTarget->DespawnOrUnsummon(DESPAWN_TIME);
227 caster->KilledMonsterCredit(newEntry);
228 }
229 }
230 }
231
232 void Register() override
233 {
234 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve_SpellScript::HandleDummy, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
235 }
236 };
237
238 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override
239 {
240 return new spell_q6124_6129_apply_salve_SpellScript();
241 }
242};

278 {
279 PrepareAuraScript(spell_q11396_11399_force_shield_arcane_purple_x3_AuraScript);
280
281 void HandleEffectApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
282 {
283 Unit* target = GetTarget();
284 target->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_PC);

287
288 void HandleEffectRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
289 {
290 GetTarget()->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_PC);
291 }
292
293 void Register() override
294 {
295 OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_q11396_11399_force_shield_arcane_purple_x3_AuraScript::HandleEffectApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
296 OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_q11396_11399_force_shield_arcane_purple_x3_AuraScript::HandleEffectRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
297 }
298
299 };

314 {

318 {
319 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_FORCE_SHIELD_ARCANE_PURPLE_X3) || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_SCOURGING_CRYSTAL_CONTROLLER))
320 return false;
321 return true;
322 }
323
324 void HandleDummy(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
325 {
326 if (Unit* target = GetExplTargetUnit())
327 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT && target->HasAura(SPELL_FORCE_SHIELD_ARCANE_PURPLE_X3))
328 // Make sure nobody else is channeling the same target

330 GetCaster()->CastSpell(target, SPELL_SCOURGING_CRYSTAL_CONTROLLER, true, GetCastItem());
331 }

334 {

590 {
591 PrepareSpellScript(spell_q12634_despawn_fruit_tosser_SpellScript);

593 bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellEntry*/) override
594 {
595 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_BANANAS_FALL_TO_GROUND) || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_ORANGE_FALLS_TO_GROUND) || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_PAPAYA_FALLS_TO_GROUND) || !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_SUMMON_ADVENTUROUS_DWARF))
